le=\"color: red;\">Yes! US</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4fbb6765ed98617cc7412582fe17c074468bb945","tid":1557052,"uid":158063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"唔係做開或者有特別技能亂咁創業好危險，同埋就算真係有野想做要計埋執左佢要幾錢埋單。"},{"pid":"f32d27f9356897794a3e9df56608c2f00169333f","tid":1557052,"uid":30272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfdffff44825d39b421bb713af312c65a3e4fd79","tid":1557052,"uid":196712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n<br />\n最重要都係地址"},{"pid":"feffd9669371fe32264344df52e2c68fe67f3b73","tid":1557052,"uid":158063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8532b26f993f497d20b7bb760b33dc178e79f798","tid":1557052,"uid":244223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30d1cc913ea9ca982c6f870100b0f9ce1913e509","tid":1557052,"uid":152790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"如果為左唔番工而去創業<br />\n冇特別有熱誠想做或熟悉既事業<br />\n<br />\n好危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"我對錢有無限熱誠，但又唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗到做邊行，但唔熟悉，想邊做邊學，咁樣危唔危險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"邊做邊學要預交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋要計執左佢要幾錢，例如租約完之前條數。最理想係搵啲位入左行先或者搵果行前輩請教下先。"},{"pid":"e951058d520bf80402eb16800ff35a6e8051e323","tid":1557052,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"而家創? 創邊個範疇先?"},{"pid":"e1446eb3f54b426a3da8c3b30a49d63adb86fee6","tid":1557052,"uid":280457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"我反而好奇點解受唔住ON9警嫂同事<br />\n走果個反而係你~~"},{"pid":"b7fcdbe787e257581cfec7b03d45128423145088","tid":1557052,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot